Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:07.96,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:121622,127961}"The Smile of Stone" opened its curtains in\Na converted underground theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:11.88,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:127961,131882}The opening performance only attracted\Nan audience of twelve,
